{"tid":1603531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[全部人入嚟] 一人一封email 煲大印尼記者單嘢上印尼領事館！！","createTime":"2019-09-29T16:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T17:32:00.000Z","uid":276267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2596d5f03a4565d3551ff167e13afa4647c2b565","tid":1603531,"uid":276267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:52:17.000Z","msg":"印尼政府奶唔奶共，我哋控制唔到<br />\n但至少send email比印尼領事館 <br />\n等佢哋知道除咗印尼國內報道，仲有好多香港人關注，要跟緊啲單嘢！！<br />\n強烈呼籲印尼以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">外交手段</span></strong>應付印尼國民在港人身安全問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n印尼話 &amp; 英文 email template:<br />\n==========================<br />\nYth. KJRI Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDengan hormat,<br />\n<br />\nHari ini, seorang reporter wanita (Veby Mega Indah) yang bekerja untuk publikasi berbahasa Indonesia, sayangnya, diserang oleh polisi Hong Kong, dengan cedera mata kanan yang dipastikan pecah dan kehilangan penglihatan. Dengan demikian, perhatian diplomatik dari konsulat Anda mengenai keamanan pribadi ribuan warganegara Indonesia di Hong Kong harus ditangani dan dikoordinasikan dengan pemerintah Cina Hong Kong.<br />\n<br />\nTerima kasih atas perhatian Anda.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/en/component/k2/1483231-20190929.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fen%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483231-20190929.htm&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=51ca04ec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fen%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483231-20190929.htm&h=9272e75c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/en/component/k2/1483231-20190929.htm</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3030864/indonesian-journalist-demands-answers-after-she-was-shot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3030864%2Findonesian-journalist-demands-answers-after-she-was-shot&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=7cfca020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3030864/indonesian-journalist-demands-answers-after-she-was-shot</a><br />\n(translation not available) <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190929/60097908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190929%2F60097908&d=WosQ6lw2L4bsKafLDhDjrbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=b5fe7542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190929%2F60097908&h=f66f6265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190929/60097908</a><br />\n<br />\nHormat kami,<br />\n(Name)<br />\nWarganegara Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\nDear Consulate General of The Republic of Indonesia in Hong Kong,<br />\n<br />\nToday, one female reporter (Veby Mega Indah) who works for an Indonesian-language publication was unfortunately attacked by the Hong Kong police, with right eye injury confirmed rupture and vision loss. Thus, diplomatic attention from your consulate regarding the personal safety of thousands of Indonesian citizens in Hong Kong would have to be addressed and coordinated with the Hong Kong Chinese government. <br />\n<br />\nThank you for your attention.<br />\n<br />\nBest regards,<br />\n(Name)<br />\nHong Kong citizen"},{"pid":"488d0ccedff07e59b1232342c1ca968a8cd38bd4","tid":1603531,"uid":276267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9773eed7a0e1572842401fad21ad957ce3ed71c7","tid":1603531,"uid":276267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:54:45.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed5f177c41fbb9911890da78d466d4aae86d41b5","tid":1603531,"uid":276267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:54:56.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9884ef4ae12d154e5b533ed0866e2a373b27b111","tid":1603531,"uid":276267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:55:24.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c927b196ae5f7fd7bd79bc2f38f58d23bff3bac","tid":1603531,"uid":276267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:55:35.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse